{"tid":1745032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"1124 有人話會扮黑衣人搞事","createTime":"2019-11-22T04:34:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-22T11:39:55.000Z","uid":289949,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"62f72dc0da7bd0ac5814b87e773170ea9aa90fbe","tid":1745032,"uid":289949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:34:21.000Z","msg":"只要票站開左3個鐘都會計算在內。<br />\n<br />\n馮驊說，只要有票站持續三小時有混亂，即停止選舉。即只要早上十點後關票站，都會計算在內。<br />\n<br />\n怪不得有建制派攪飲早茶團，今次調轉來，係朝早7點投完票先一齊去飲茶。<br />\n<br />\n政府呢招果然絕呀！<br />\n <br />\n同埋只要建制早上一夠票，即刻派人扮黑衣人在選舉站前搗亂，然後大有藉口把選舉煞停，咁就 sure win.....<br />\n<br />\n請大家7:30去投票<br />\n<br />\nSource tg"},{"pid":"24f3442f2b51f67256b716a540ee4a9d440cf2a6","tid":1745032,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T04:37:20.000Z","msg":"出返抗爭者聲明好似上次清真咁"},{"pid":"8452dbd39b2c56b498a9945e39b1986600b7c000","tid":1745032,"uid":209382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:03:00.000Z","msg":"【抗爭者區議會免責宣示】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745587\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745587</a>"},{"pid":"4b4a59f2dd96dc41953b4145f40a603a15a53d45","tid":1745032,"uid":279401,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T10:09:22.000Z","msg":"1124一定要全民都投建制派<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1745329\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1745329</a>"},{"pid":"3186ded1a145261ff81237d5d3c20e6decef1591","tid":1745032,"uid":169048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-22T11:39:55.000Z","msg":"咁要奉議員號召止暴制亂啦"}]}